 http://android-dev-tips-and-tricks.blogspot.in/2014/02/creating-card-ui.html
 http://myandroidtuts.blogspot.in/2013/12/android-card-layout.html
 https://www.androidhive.info/2016/05/android-working-with-card-view-and-recycler-view/
 http://www.truiton.com/2015/03/android-cardview-example/
 https://stackoverflow.com/questions/30751870/can-one-use-cardview-for-listView-item-and-how
 https://www.androidhive.info/2016/01/android-working-with-recycler-view/
